attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Incredible ground up new construction townhomes in optimal South Boston location. Built by renowned firm Catamount Builders, these 3 units will live like single family homes, with garage parking, thoughtfully designed spacious layouts, and private roof decks. Impeccable attention to detail with intricate millwork, custom cabinetry, stone counters and baths as well as high end Thermador appliance package. This unit boasts 3 bedrooms, an additional study, 3.5 baths, and ample storage throughout. Hardwood floors, designer tile selections, central web controlled HVAC, in unit laundry and a plethora of closet space compliment the open and spacious layouts.2nd outdoor tandem space adjacent to garage possible and perfect location just a block from bustling Broadway make this a must see property.
